query:
INSERT INTO tags (id, project_id, name, color)
            SELECT gen_random_uuid(), $1, name, color
            FROM UNNEST($2::text[], $3::text[]) AS t(name, color)
            RETURNING
                id          AS "id!: Uuid",
                project_id  AS "project_id!: Uuid",
                name        AS "name!",
                color       AS "color!"
